00:08:48.920 --> 00:08:51.130 align:middle line:10%
There was a time when I
was studying biology--

00:08:51.130 --> 00:08:54.850 align:middle line:10%
again, back in
the 1960s, 1970s--

00:08:54.850 --> 00:08:58.360 align:middle line:10%
when I was taught
that the brain has

00:08:58.360 --> 00:09:00.130 align:middle line:10%
very specific parts
of the brain that

00:09:00.130 --> 00:09:02.980 align:middle line:10%
do very specific functions.

00:09:02.980 --> 00:09:05.230 align:middle line:10%
And if we lose that
part of the brain,

00:09:05.230 --> 00:09:07.270 align:middle line:10%
