00:09:16.940 --> 00:09:21.640 align:middle line:84%
It doesn't work quite the way
we had been led to believe.

00:09:21.640 --> 00:09:25.000 align:middle line:84%
During their experiments,
they showed that our brain

00:09:25.000 --> 00:09:26.980 align:middle line:90%
is holographic as well.

00:09:26.980 --> 00:09:29.590 align:middle line:84%
What happened was that
there was research

00:09:29.590 --> 00:09:31.510 align:middle line:84%
that was being done
when laboratory

00:09:31.510 --> 00:09:34.600 align:middle line:84%
animals, for example, would lose
a certain part of their brain

00:09:34.600 --> 00:09:36.970 align:middle line:84%
that had been
believed to perform

00:09:36.970 --> 00:09:38.366 align:middle line:90%
only a certain function.

00:09:38.366 --> 00:09:40.990 align:middle line:84%
So maybe there is a part of the
brain that was used for speech,

00:09:40.990 --> 00:09:44.330 align:middle line:84%
or part of the brain that
was used for motor function.

00:09:44.330 --> 00:09:46.450 align:middle line:84%
The old thinking says,
if that part of the brain

00:09:46.450 --> 00:09:49.690 align:middle line:84%
no longer exists, that
that function is lost.

00:09:49.690 --> 00:09:51.970 align:middle line:84%
