in the experiments.

00:09:51.970 --> 00:09:53.920 align:middle line:84%
When a specific
part of the brain

00:09:53.920 --> 00:09:56.650 align:middle line:84%
was damaged, or in some
cases even removed,

00:09:56.650 --> 00:10:01.360 align:middle line:84%
