00:10:06.160 --> 00:10:11.380 align:middle line:84%
This led the scientists to
hypothesize-- maybe the brain

00:10:11.380 --> 00:10:12.850 align:middle line:90%
is not as linear as we think.

00:10:12.850 --> 00:10:14.710 align:middle line:90%
Maybe it is holographic.

00:10:14.710 --> 00:10:16.150 align:middle line:90%
So they began to do experiments.

00:10:16.150 --> 00:10:18.670 align:middle line:84%
And I'll tell you
exactly how this works.

00:10:18.670 --> 00:10:20.560 align:middle line:90%
